Package edu.csus.plugin.securecodingassistant.compilation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InsecureCodeSegment
    Represents a segment of source code that is potentially insecure.
    NodeVisitor
    A custom ASTVisitor for the Secure Coding Assistant that checks each ASTNode on the AST (Abstract Syntax Tree) to see if there has been a rule violation.
    SecureCompilationParticipant
    Uses the NodeVisitor to check each ASTNode to see if an IRule has been violated.
